main event: Two bright red lights were observed making a humming sound before moving rapidly and changing direction overhead.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 20 minutes.,The lights were stationary for about 1 minute before moving.,Witnesses described the lights as very bright reddish-orange.,The observer had previously watched missile firings from Cape Kennedy.,The lights flew overhead and then disappeared to the northeast.
witness description: Civilian and military sources reported the sighting.
